* [[Bill Ponsford]]
* [[Victor Trumper]]
* [[Neil Harvey]]
* [[Allan Border]]
* [[Arthur Morris]]
* [[Bill Woodfull]]
* [[Greg Chappell]]
* [[Stan McCabe]]
* [[Ian Chappell]]
* [[Lindsay Hassett]]
* [[Clem Hill]]
* [[Bob Simpson (cricket)|Bob Simpson]]
* [[Steve Waugh]]
|
'''[[All-rounder]]s'''
* [[Keith Miller]]
* [[Warwick Armstrong]]
* [[Alan Davidson]]
* [[Monty Noble]]
* [[Charlie Macartney]]
* [[Richie Benaud]]
